OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSupermarkets told to make  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpricing clearer            
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Supermarkets have been told to make    
OL,6, their pricing clearer to help shoppers 
OL,7, find the best deals.                   
OL,9,FThe Competition and Markets Authority  
OL,10,F(CMA) said unclear pricing could be    
OL,11,Fhampering people's ability to compare  
OL,12,Fproducts.                              
OL,14,FThe watchdog said retailers should     
OL,15,F"make the necessary changes" and also  
OL,16,Fcalled on the government to bring in   
OL,17,Freforms to tighten the law itself.     
OL,19,FIt added that soaring food prices were 
OL,20,Fnot being driven by weak competition.  
